{"tid":2292050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府消息：推行大灣區青年就業計劃　支援青年到大灣區工作一年","createTime":"2020-11-19T07:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T00:37:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b639adbfe9967812a580d4c8320d68b12c8ee03c","tid":2292050,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"《星島日報》引述消息報道，特首林鄭月娥將在11月25日發表新一份《施政報告》時宣布大灣區青年就業計劃。<br />\n<br />\n據報，該就業計劃將支援數千香港青年到大灣區城市工作一年，職位種類包括科技、金融業等，設有年齡限制，每月工資可達1.5萬至2萬元，政府將會提供資助，惟實際細節尚未確定。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，有關計劃將以配對形式運作，騰訊（0700）等多家大企業已表示感興趣提供職位。"},{"pid":"773e39b5fc413ffce2fc530e7a75147039b0201a","tid":2292050,"uid":59618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abc443dce6efc8d9142a18981208da9441275c1","tid":2292050,"uid":38904,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"得15k-20k我使撚返去做咩"},{"pid":"38d9be9d271fd5ef726f09612db4b858af5bbb56","tid":2292050,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:01:27.000Z","msg":"大灣區投資疑墮騙局，逾百港人苦主涉款4500萬，政總請願盼特首跟進<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gppggS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gppggS</a>"},{"pid":"356933ee80eef42c97ffd0e201eededeb0aee958","tid":2292050,"uid":68689,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"香港呢家失業率咁高 你唔搞好香港本土就業問題<br />\n走去送走班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7edb65b495345f25f7cc4d43fafecd4c5261d2e","tid":2292050,"uid":286897,"like":4,"disli